- Valid size entries are those with a size identifier greater than 0; 
- US women's clothing sizes refer to the standard sizing system used in the United States for women's clothing; 
- Clothing categories can include tops, bottoms, dresses, outerwear, etc.

- Average measurements are used to determine the standard size for each clothing type; 
- The query assumes that the measurements are either in centimeters or inches; 
- The '86-91cm' chest measurement is a special case and is handled separately in the query.
